---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Reformer Classes | HALM Wellness">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Reformer Classes</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">Join our dynamic group reformer pilates sessions for strength, flexibility, and core conditioning.</p>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>Our reformer classes combine traditional Pilates principles with modern exercise science to create a challenging, full-body workout that improves strength, flexibility, and posture. Each class is kept small to ensure proper form and individual attention.</p>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Class Levels</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-4">
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Beginner</h3>
          <p>Perfect for those new to reformer pilates. Learn the fundamentals and basic movements.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Intermediate</h3>
          <p>Build on the basics with more challenging sequences and variations.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Advanced</h3>
          <p>Challenge yourself with complex movements and flowing sequences.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Schedule & Booking</h2>
      <p>View our current class schedule and book your spot online.</p>
      
      <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="/schedule" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary-dark transition">View Schedule</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
